     H            Y.
      ** UEXR46A ***************************************************
      *  UPDATE SHIP DATE IN AB#EP60                               *
      *  JW     2021.09.20                                         *
      **************************************************************
      *  CALLING SEQ.                                              *
      *                    CALL 'UEXR46A'
      *                    PARM           $SHID  10
      *                    PARM           $GDATE  8
      *                    PARM           $BDATE  8
      *   IN  $SHID  10A  SHIPMENT ID                              *
      *       $GDATE  8A  GOOD DATE (ACTUAL DATE)                  *
      *       $BDATE  8A  BAD  DATE (TOBE CHANGED)                 *
      **************************************************************
     FAB#EP60 UF  E           K        DISK
      ***********************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $SHID  10
     C                     PARM           $GDATE  8
     C                     PARM           $BDATE  8
     C                     MOVEL$BDATE    @BDATE  80
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ AB#EP60                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           E1SHID    IFNE $SHID
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           E1NOHZ    IFNE @BDATE
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL$GDATE    E1NOHZ
     C                     UPDATAB#EP601
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
